suncertify.db.data
Class FileMetaData

java.lang.Object
  suncertify.db.data.FileMetaData

public final class FileMetaData
extends java.lang.Object

Metadata of DB files. This includes all fields in the file prologue and schema description section. Provides methods to calculate aggregated properties (e.g. record length, offset of a record within the file).
